title: Consistent mid LF Duo/Flex
body:
Win lane almost every game, new to oce as i've just moved here from EUW.

Looking for a confident Duo or Flex players, dont care about the rank just your mindset & ability to snowball a lead.

replies.body: Hey I am I zed main who plays mid. I win my lane most of the time. I will add you.
Hey I'm a jungle main if you want to message me for some duo. I have a good friendly attitude and know how to win the game
